{"tid":2108512,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"埃及士兵入境後確診 泰國暫停所有飛機降落","createTime":"2020-07-14T14:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T15:07:34.000Z","uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e5632923c6a6d6db2a4567ab3cffad14c044c395","tid":2108512,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"埃及士兵入境後確診 泰國暫停所有飛機降落<br />\n2020-07-14 HKT 21:12<br />\n<br />\n&quot;泰國暫停所有飛機降落，因為一批埃及軍人在自我隔離期間，擅自走到當地一個商場，其中一人檢測後實證確診型肺炎。埃及駐泰國大使館就事件造成的影響表示遺憾和同情。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;泰國已經連續50日沒有本地確診新型肺炎個案...&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537735-20200714.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537735-20200714.htm&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuMFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=d1a1cee3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537735-20200714.htm&h=a36c39a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537735-20200714.htm</a>"},{"pid":"575f16c87916f96e5e805c5a72a87d3c40a64bcc","tid":2108512,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T14:59:47.000Z","msg":"泰國連續50日咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d62ae0ce2f286cc24bb79ee0cb88bbb1f0f219","tid":2108512,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"575f16c87916f96e5e805c5a72a87d3c40a64bcc","tid":2108512,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T14:59:47.000Z","msg":"泰國連續50日咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:06:56.000Z","msg":"但檢測數量少:  8,648/1M pop<br />\nvs HK 50,226/1M pop"},{"pid":"44782a72aa111ac0f2b129ab057e8ef4702a8ebe","tid":2108512,"ui